# UI Component Development Standards

## Framework Requirements
- Komponenty UI twórz w oparciu o Tailwind, ShadCN, Radix
- NIE używaj klas CSS bez kontekstu
- Wszystkie komponenty muszą być responsive (mobile-first)
- Dark/Light theme support wymagany

## Component Architecture  
- Functional components z TypeScript strict mode
- Proper prop interfaces z JSDoc documentation
- Error boundaries dla complex components
- Accessibility compliance (WCAG 2.1 AA)

## AI-Specific UI Patterns
- Real-time streaming response interfaces
- Model health indicators z animations
- Voice input z waveform visualization
- Smart suggestions z contextual tooltips
- Vector search results z relevance scores

## Performance Requirements
- React.memo dla expensive components
- Lazy loading dla off-screen elements
- Bundle size optimization
- Core Web Vitals compliance

## Three UI Modes Support
- Simple Workspace: Dashboard z 4 panels
- Creative Canvas: Drag & drop widgets
- Advanced Wizard: Step-by-step flow

Ensure każdy komponent działa we wszystkich trzech modes.
